               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Durrat al-tāj li-ghurrat al-Dubāj by Quṭb al-Dīn Maḥmūd ibn Z̤iyāʾ al-Dīn Masʿūd al-Shīrāzī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008111185" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1445-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Excerpt from a large encyclopaedia of sciences, here comprising the fourth jumlah dealing with mathematics and geometry, compiled by 
                <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100167332137.0x000001 viaf_236145542748996641711" role="aut">Quṭb al-Dīn Maḥmūd ibn Z̤iyāʾ al-Dīn Masʿūd al-Shīrāzī</persName>(d. 710/1310), a student of 
                <persName key="viaf_12392936" role="oth">Naṣīr al-Dīn Ṭūsī</persName>.
                        </p>
                        <p>The treatise is dedicated to 
                <persName key="person_f8109" role="dte">Dubāj</persName>, the local ruler of Gīlān province.
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end.</p>
                        <p>Naskh and nastaʿlīq.</p>
                        <p>Diagrams.</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_236145542748996641711">Quṭb al-Dīn Maḥmūd ibn Z̤iyāʾ al-Dīn Masʿūd al-Shīrāzī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_236145542748996641711">قطب الدّين محمود ابن ضيأ الدّين مسعود الشّيرازى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_11053">Durrat al-tāj li-ghurrat al-Dubāj</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_11053">درّة التّاج لغرّة الدّباج</title>
